Package: obesitychances
Title: Calculate Your Obesity Probabilities
Description: Perform accurate calculations to determine your probailiites of getting obsese 
             using three metrics - BMI Calculator, Waist To Hip Ratio and Waist To Height Ratio.
             Afterwards, compute the obseity status of your inputs (0%, 33%, 66%, 100%)
Version: 1.0
